snippet.title: Pathogenesis: Overcome. Teaser 2020
snippet.description:
Pathogenesis: Overcome
Hardcore story-driven Action RPG about those who survived after a global pandemic on the territory of Leningradskaya Oblast, Russia. A story about finding your place in a destroyed world, where the greatest danger does not come from the infected. 
Release Date: Autumn 2021

Music: World Beyond
https://www.worldbeyond.net/
